      <div class="subNavigator4_a">
        <div>
          <div>
            <p>1)Stylish Design</p>
            <p>Women E-bikes are marvelously designed. Women like fashion and style in everything. That's why women's e-bikes have some unexpected curves and impressive designs.</p>
          </div>
